<A>__{the waves begin to grow, the ocean turns a slate gray. far above him, great frigate birds circle. suddenly one dives on a booby which has caught a fish. the great frigate bird swoops all around the booby until, panicked, it drops the fish, which plummets toward the sea. with a graceful dive, the huge bird grabs the fish and then soars up on a thermal, high into the sky. lightning flashes back and forth across the horizon, which is turning black and dark. thunder rolls.}
